{"tid":1630074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"需要港島大遊行主要原因","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:15.000Z","uid":41744,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a5d9c25f442aba832c0fc7c3332791d1ed382b4","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"十八區同大遊行既最大分別<br />\n係遊行有大量震撼 顯眼 易見易明 既實體文宣<br />\n大量旗幟 海報 表達我地訴求<br />\n十八區冇咁大迴響主要大家好少帶文宣出去<br />\n傳媒畫面冇辦法放大我地訴求 <br />\n所有野我地都要和理非backup<br />\n俾人知我地冇失焦 一樣對準五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以黎緊既遍地開花 麻煩大家帶上文宣</span><br />\n唔好怕麻煩<br />\n集合&gt;舉牌&gt;裝飾/裝修<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9813e58a4daa1d8e17f68aab25b4cfeaff0400dc","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"同黑警對峙前 一定要放大所有文宣做support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3726085cdafc422d96093650ed12ce26ed733f8","tid":1630074,"uid":129783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"c27975c7d014beb2b97ebc7610d3f47e94d2a1fe","tid":1630074,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">狗狗真係好驚快閃行動<br />\n班狗平時喺連登行動post/TG收風早定部署<br />\n一轉快閃模式佢地已經失去行動方向<br />\n佢地好驚小team行動好驚俾人圍<br />\n所以班狗要時間部署集結好先一齊行動<br />\n遊行完請唔好戀戰<br />\n各散去各區做快閃</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BE WATER </span></strong>"},{"pid":"238bdc732d4196347ad47a4d6313ffe28ce3b193","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"黎緊既遍地開花 麻煩大家帶上文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7992549bfbb94bb1f671e6cd2913a83df80eea1","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"黎緊既遍地開花 麻煩大家帶上文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d806b0e72594dcad23d47fa8926a05c74dd963f1","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"大家對以武制暴 裝修等有少少反感覺<br />\n主要係呢排新聞真係少左文宣報導<br />\n大家千其唔好怕麻煩<br />\n特別係和理非<br />\n出黎唔單止要充人數<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲要舉牌舉文宣啊</span></span><br />\n咁勇武先可以放心做野"},{"pid":"d6205f8c834cb0db337ccb02cd366114a0095987","tid":1630074,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"而家有晒理由比勇武手足做野"},{"pid":"f0f6c7afd70829de87422de561706b13ea2b1b9e","tid":1630074,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"fcc4598407b8d5910c36beb3893c1a054e30784d","tid":1630074,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"以後有gear勇武唔好去港島"},{"pid":"0085079296ec0379a223cace2c5111b9636bea63","tid":1630074,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"但代價太大，每次百萬行都一定起碼100人被捕，<br />\n不如唔好再搞"},{"pid":"3aa2067711de01550f47c2858be198c7bfd00598","tid":1630074,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"今日既焦點已經比馬蹄爽同誤燒記者搶哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8d7d5db7c5d4d642a332ad5d4e250d6bea34be","tid":1630074,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶住文宣遍地開花 取代大遊行</span></span>"}]}